Package: odooctl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, docker-compose | docker-compose-v2
Recommends: docker.io
Description: CLI tool for managing Odoo Docker development environments
 odooctl is a command-line tool that simplifies the creation and management
 of Odoo development environments using Docker.
 .
 Features:
  - Docker environment management (create, run, stop, reset, status, logs)
  - Module scaffolding and installation
  - Multi-environment support per project
  - Auto-discovery of Python dependencies from manifests
  - Port conflict detection and auto-resolution
